com.juraj.hdbs.querying.language

Class GlobalSQLBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.juraj.hdbs.querying.language.GlobalSQLBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GlobalSQLListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class GlobalSQLBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements GlobalSQLListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of GlobalSQLListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
